      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SENTOSAR (10) has come up against stronger company at Menangle in two outings since tackling the Gold Chalice series at Bathurst where he was runner-up in the consolation. Has had four weeks off but was kept ticking over with a trial win. Tricky draws but has recorded a win and a placing in two tries at this circuit and distance so is better placed. SEASIDE DRIVE (7) enjoys a class drop after tackling the Nutrien Classic Sales race series at Wagga. Beat SENTOSAR home when they clashed at Menangle prior and she draws for a trail. COMPLETE STRANGER (6) is another coming off the Nutrien series and went into that off back-to-back placing's so is better placed. CANTPLZA MALTEEZA (9) comes into contention after coming from this barrier and scoring last week at this circuit and distance. FEARFUL (8) draws on the back row this time but cannot be ruled out after some good efforts including a win here two back.",
